WEBVTT

00:00:43.560 --> 00:00:45.290
Qianfan, I'm going to kill you.

00:00:46.720 --> 00:00:48.450
Are you crazy? I'm your father.

00:00:48.840 --> 00:00:49.960
No, you're not.

00:00:50.160 --> 00:00:51.760
You're that man in black.

00:00:52.920 --> 00:00:54.800
You've done so many evil things.

00:00:55.120 --> 00:00:57.180
How dare you call yourself my father?

00:00:58.560 --> 00:00:59.760
Seize him!

00:01:06.160 --> 00:01:08.360
You talk too much.

00:01:11.600 --> 00:01:13.760
Go tell it to the King of Hell.

00:01:27.360 --> 00:01:28.200
Yiyu!

00:01:30.280 --> 00:01:32.000
I'm sorry.

00:01:33.440 --> 00:01:34.080
You!

00:01:37.039 --> 00:01:39.039
I'll fight you to the death!

00:01:48.880 --> 00:01:50.720
Get rid of him completely.

00:01:50.920 --> 00:01:51.440
Yes.

00:01:56.280 --> 00:01:57.680
Why don't you kill me?

00:01:59.479 --> 00:02:01.160
You're my daughter.

00:02:01.600 --> 00:02:03.440
Why would I want to kill you?

00:02:04.280 --> 00:02:06.320
You're not my father at all.

00:02:11.120 --> 00:02:13.450
A married daughter is like spilled water.

00:02:13.600 --> 00:02:15.260
Taking sides with outsiders.

00:02:15.440 --> 00:02:17.360
So all these years,

00:02:17.600 --> 00:02:19.520
I've raised an ungrateful child.

00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:21.360
You raised me all these years

00:02:21.880 --> 00:02:23.440
just to use me as

00:02:23.480 --> 00:02:26.000
a pawn you could manipulate at will?

00:02:26.360 --> 00:02:27.600
To hurt others.

00:02:28.280 --> 00:02:30.600
You're absolutely despicable.

00:02:31.320 --> 00:02:34.480
You killed my birth parents with your own hands.

00:02:35.160 --> 00:02:38.240
And here you are pretending to be a loving father.

00:02:39.280 --> 00:02:40.200
Bah!

00:02:41.640 --> 00:02:43.079
My dear daughter,

00:02:43.320 --> 00:02:45.050
you shouldn't say such things.

00:02:45.360 --> 00:02:48.760
Your parents were meddling in affairs that didn't concern them.

00:02:48.760 --> 00:02:51.000
And now you're just like them.

00:02:52.040 --> 00:02:54.760
You've done so many shameful things.

00:02:55.880 --> 00:02:58.800
You even committed adultery behind the master and mistress's backs.

00:02:58.800 --> 00:03:00.240
You killed my parents

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:01.480
just because

00:03:01.520 --> 00:03:04.320
they knew about all your dirty secrets?

00:03:06.760 --> 00:03:08.220
You're talking nonsense!

00:03:09.760 --> 00:03:11.240
Mrs. Liu.

00:03:11.880 --> 00:03:14.040
She loved me.

00:03:15.040 --> 00:03:17.040
I'm the one she should have married.

00:03:19.880 --> 00:03:21.400
Why?

00:03:21.680 --> 00:03:24.760
I built everything from nothing with Liu Muzhi.

00:03:25.520 --> 00:03:28.880
Why is he the respected Mr. Liu?

00:03:29.320 --> 00:03:32.240
While I'm just his workhorse.

00:03:33.800 --> 00:03:34.960
It's not fair.

00:03:35.680 --> 00:03:36.960
The woman I love.

00:03:37.880 --> 00:03:39.480
He took her too.

00:03:39.960 --> 00:03:41.160
I can't accept it.

00:03:41.320 --> 00:03:43.240
Stop fooling yourself.

00:03:45.880 --> 00:03:48.480
Someone as despicable as you.

00:03:49.480 --> 00:03:52.400
How could Mrs. Liu ever love you?

00:03:55.520 --> 00:03:56.960
What do you know?

00:03:59.800 --> 00:04:01.660
Liu Muzhi left on a business trip.

00:04:01.680 --> 00:04:03.320
He never returned.

00:04:03.880 --> 00:04:05.210
No news of him anywhere.

00:04:07.120 --> 00:04:08.160
People said.

00:04:08.680 --> 00:04:09.680
He met with a shipwreck.

00:04:09.680 --> 00:04:10.960
And died abroad.

00:04:12.680 --> 00:04:13.880
Mrs. Liu.

00:04:16.519 --> 00:04:17.600
My Yaqing.

00:04:20.240 --> 00:04:21.880
Was heartbroken.

00:04:22.960 --> 00:04:25.240
I was the one who took care of her.

00:04:25.320 --> 00:04:26.320
I told her.

00:04:26.320 --> 00:04:28.760
I would be her support from then on.

00:04:30.880 --> 00:04:31.760
That day.

00:04:32.880 --> 00:04:33.600
That night.

00:04:33.680 --> 00:04:35.680
We drank a lot.

00:04:37.159 --> 00:04:39.880
What a blissful night it was.

00:04:41.120 --> 00:04:42.600
Those days.

00:04:43.159 --> 00:04:46.240
Were the happiest time of my life.

00:04:46.600 --> 00:04:47.680
I asked someone

00:04:48.320 --> 00:04:51.320
to custom-make a pair of gemstone rings in Shanghai.

00:04:51.480 --> 00:04:53.680
They were meant to be our tokens of love.

00:04:57.320 --> 00:05:00.360
You were just taking advantage of the situation.

00:05:02.360 --> 00:05:03.200
You.

00:05:06.240 --> 00:05:07.770
But who would have thought.

00:05:08.200 --> 00:05:11.040
Right on Liu Silin's 18th birthday,

00:05:11.160 --> 00:05:12.640
he actually came back.

00:05:13.200 --> 00:05:16.680
He came to celebrate that brat son of his.

00:05:16.920 --> 00:05:18.960
Today is my son Silin's birthday.

00:05:19.080 --> 00:05:20.920
Thank you all for coming.

00:05:20.920 --> 00:05:21.800
Have a drink.

00:05:22.920 --> 00:05:23.640
Thank you.

00:05:24.240 --> 00:05:24.880
Come.

00:05:26.240 --> 00:05:27.080
Mother.

00:05:30.520 --> 00:05:32.040
Please be seated, everyone.

00:05:32.040 --> 00:05:34.600
Such a young boy, so precious to him.

00:05:35.520 --> 00:05:36.480
My Yaqing.

00:05:37.040 --> 00:05:38.480
When she saw him,

00:05:38.680 --> 00:05:40.040
she was speechless.

00:05:46.480 --> 00:05:47.880
She hanged herself.

00:06:18.520 --> 00:06:19.960
My Yaqing,

00:06:20.080 --> 00:06:21.080
do you know?

00:06:21.400 --> 00:06:23.360
She was pregnant with my child.

00:06:24.360 --> 00:06:25.480
I will make

00:06:26.040 --> 00:06:27.680
Liu Muzhi

00:06:29.080 --> 00:06:30.600
Liu Silin

00:06:30.760 --> 00:06:31.960
pay blood for blood.

00:06:32.360 --> 00:06:33.640
Shut up!

00:06:35.040 --> 00:06:37.920
You're utterly despicable,

00:06:38.320 --> 00:06:41.920
saying such vile things so shamelessly.

00:06:42.760 --> 00:06:45.159
I've called you father for so many years.

00:06:45.800 --> 00:06:47.480
I feel sick

00:06:47.960 --> 00:06:48.920
and disgusted.

00:06:52.080 --> 00:06:54.760
If you have the guts, kill me now.

00:06:56.200 --> 00:06:59.040
Otherwise, I'll haunt you even as a ghost.

00:06:59.480 --> 00:07:00.800
Last time,

00:07:01.240 --> 00:07:03.480
Liu Silin's aim was poor.

00:07:04.320 --> 00:07:05.920
He didn't hit my vital spots.

00:07:06.400 --> 00:07:08.960
Only slightly injured my hand.

00:07:09.200 --> 00:07:10.080
Look.

00:07:13.240 --> 00:07:14.880
I should have known.

00:07:15.800 --> 00:07:17.960
You were the one in black that night.

00:07:18.600 --> 00:07:19.640
As expected

00:07:20.080 --> 00:07:22.800
of a good daughter I, Qianfan, raised.

00:07:24.880 --> 00:07:26.240
You actually knew.

00:07:27.200 --> 00:07:29.680
Using a fake secret letter to trick me.

00:07:43.600 --> 00:07:44.480
After them!

00:07:53.600 --> 00:07:54.360
Butler!

00:07:54.480 --> 00:07:55.760
What are you doing?

00:07:56.880 --> 00:07:58.080
Someone broke into the Liu mansion.

00:07:58.080 --> 00:08:00.210
The young master sent us to catch them.

00:08:02.080 --> 00:08:02.480
Hey!

00:08:02.600 --> 00:08:04.730
I think I saw someone running that way.

00:08:05.360 --> 00:08:06.080
Let's go!

00:08:09.480 --> 00:08:11.040
What a pity.

00:08:12.680 --> 00:08:15.080
That was your last chance.

00:08:15.480 --> 00:08:16.520
Yet you all

00:08:17.080 --> 00:08:18.540
let it slip away so easily.

00:08:20.240 --> 00:08:22.600
Everyone in the Liu mansion,

00:08:23.200 --> 00:08:24.600
they're all fools.

00:08:24.760 --> 00:08:27.320
I've been playing them like puppets.

00:08:27.360 --> 00:08:28.880
They're not fools.

00:08:30.160 --> 00:08:31.080
It's you.

00:08:31.240 --> 00:08:33.159
You used them.

00:08:33.320 --> 00:08:35.960
You betrayed their trust.

00:08:36.760 --> 00:08:39.080
You hurt them.

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:41.400
Someone like you

00:08:42.200 --> 00:08:44.200
deserves to burn in hell.

00:08:46.320 --> 00:08:47.640
Go ahead, curse me.

00:08:48.640 --> 00:08:49.960
Shout it out.

00:08:50.080 --> 00:08:51.640
Let it all out.

00:08:53.200 --> 00:08:54.600
Kill me then!

00:08:54.680 --> 00:08:56.920
If you have the guts, kill me now.

00:08:58.200 --> 00:08:59.920
Why would I kill you?

00:09:00.080 --> 00:09:01.880
Killing you would be pointless.

00:09:01.960 --> 00:09:03.800
You're still useful to me.

00:09:03.880 --> 00:09:05.210
What are you going to do?

00:09:06.760 --> 00:09:08.080
I'm going to make

00:09:08.200 --> 00:09:09.600
Liu Silin

00:09:10.360 --> 00:09:11.920
suffer beyond endurance.

00:09:24.920 --> 00:09:25.680
Yiyu

00:09:28.240 --> 00:09:29.040
Caiyue

00:09:30.120 --> 00:09:30.920
Caiyue

00:09:33.000 --> 00:09:33.730
Young Master

00:09:33.800 --> 00:09:35.400
Where is the Young Mistress?

00:09:35.480 --> 00:09:37.480
The Young Mistress left last night.

00:09:37.920 --> 00:09:39.040
She hasn't returned yet.

00:09:39.040 --> 00:09:40.600
Did she say where she went?

00:09:40.840 --> 00:09:42.160
She said she had some family matters

00:09:42.160 --> 00:09:43.240
to take care of.

00:09:47.160 --> 00:09:47.960
Young Master.

00:09:48.800 --> 00:09:51.260
Young Master, it's the head butler calling.

00:09:55.600 --> 00:09:56.320
Qianfan.

00:09:56.360 --> 00:09:58.160
Yiyu is in my hands now.

00:09:58.800 --> 00:10:00.130
What are you going to do?

00:10:00.320 --> 00:10:01.480
How is Yiyu?

00:10:01.800 --> 00:10:03.600
She came to me herself.

00:10:03.720 --> 00:10:05.250
You can't blame me for that.

00:10:05.600 --> 00:10:07.040
Listen to me, Qianfan.

00:10:07.400 --> 00:10:08.960
If you dare harm Yiyu in any way,

00:10:08.960 --> 00:10:10.290
I'll tear you to pieces.

00:10:10.600 --> 00:10:12.060
Release her immediately.

00:10:12.800 --> 00:10:14.120
My young master,

00:10:14.280 --> 00:10:15.280
don't panic.

00:10:15.920 --> 00:10:17.720
Yiyu is still fine.

00:10:18.480 --> 00:10:19.680
If you want to see her,

00:10:20.160 --> 00:10:21.690
come to my house right away.

00:10:24.520 --> 00:10:25.200
Qianfan.

00:10:25.600 --> 00:10:26.560
Qianfan.

00:10:38.600 --> 00:10:39.440
Yiyu.

00:10:39.680 --> 00:10:40.480
Yiyu.

00:10:41.160 --> 00:10:42.000
Yiyu.

00:10:42.920 --> 00:10:45.000
Qianfan, Qianfan.

00:10:45.560 --> 00:10:47.000
Get out here right now!

00:10:48.000 --> 00:10:48.800
Silin.

00:10:51.560 --> 00:10:52.360
Yiyu.

00:10:55.040 --> 00:10:55.800
Silin.

00:10:57.360 --> 00:10:58.600
Let Yiyu go.

00:11:00.840 --> 00:11:01.500
Don't move.

00:11:02.600 --> 00:11:04.000
Move and I'll kill her.

00:11:04.840 --> 00:11:06.680
If you agree to my terms,

00:11:07.680 --> 00:11:08.920
I'll let her go.

00:11:09.360 --> 00:11:10.490
If you release Yiyu,

00:11:10.920 --> 00:11:12.600
I'll agree to anything.

00:11:13.040 --> 00:11:14.440
Put the gun down first.

00:11:18.480 --> 00:11:19.280
Put it down.

00:11:21.120 --> 00:11:22.160
Silin, don't.

00:11:28.000 --> 00:11:29.480
Kick the gun over to me.

00:11:30.600 --> 00:11:31.240
Hurry up.

00:11:35.360 --> 00:11:36.160
Silin.

00:11:37.000 --> 00:11:37.800
Silin.

00:11:41.600 --> 00:11:42.920
Liu Silin

00:11:43.360 --> 00:11:44.560
Young Master Liu.

00:11:45.440 --> 00:11:46.900
So you've fallen this low.

00:11:48.040 --> 00:11:50.160
You've really disappointed me.

00:11:50.560 --> 00:11:52.560
Weren't you supposed to be so great?

00:11:53.160 --> 00:11:54.680
Weren't you so proud?

00:11:55.360 --> 00:11:57.480
Look at you now.

00:11:57.680 --> 00:11:59.440
All for a woman.

00:12:00.680 --> 00:12:02.680
I truly despise you.

00:12:02.920 --> 00:12:06.160
You're just as worthless as your dead father.

00:12:09.280 --> 00:12:11.000
I really can't understand.

00:12:12.360 --> 00:12:14.360
How Yaqing

00:12:15.160 --> 00:12:18.240
could ever marry that bastard father of yours.

00:12:18.560 --> 00:12:21.220
And then gave birth to a little bastard like you.

00:12:21.800 --> 00:12:24.560
Your father should have died at sea long ago.

00:12:24.680 --> 00:12:27.160
Then Yaqing wouldn't have killed herself.

00:12:27.480 --> 00:12:30.280
So you're the one who drove my mother to suicide.

00:12:30.920 --> 00:12:32.600
You bastard.

00:12:32.680 --> 00:12:34.360
My father thought you were loyal.

00:12:34.360 --> 00:12:36.160
He always treated you like a brother.

00:12:36.160 --> 00:12:36.720
Why?

00:12:37.000 --> 00:12:38.000
Why?

00:12:39.600 --> 00:12:40.480
Silin

00:12:42.680 --> 00:12:44.480
Don't hurt Silin.

00:12:49.360 --> 00:12:50.920
You don't know yet, do you?

00:12:51.920 --> 00:12:53.160
This woman

00:12:53.360 --> 00:12:55.220
is the one I convinced your father

00:12:55.480 --> 00:12:57.440
to place by your side.

00:13:16.200 --> 00:13:16.680
Yu

